## 🌍 Potential Impact

> 🎯 The global AI fraud detection market is projected to grow to **$65B+ by 2034**.  
GraphGuard has the potential to become a **commercial SaaS** platform for:
- Banks & digital wallets
- E-commerce marketplaces
- Crypto exchanges
- Insurance and loan platforms

Post-hackathon, GraphGuard can evolve into a **real-time fraud analytics engine** with explainable AI and federated learning across institutions.

